room_title: Escape room "The Unsolved Case" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
room_description: You and your family were the victims of an awful crime. The lead detective has just phoned you and said that the evidence against the main suspect won't stand up in court, and they're letting him go in an hour. You decide to take matters into your own hands and sneak into the detective's office, but you've accidentally locked yourself in! Will you manage to find enough evidence to prove the suspect's guilt and break out in time?
